│ post-dominate) where %4 was inserted. This points at incorrect Builder        │
│ insertion point management during SLP's rebuild of insertelement/shuffle      │
│ chains.\n\n3. Root Cause Analysis:\nIn SLPVectorizer.cpp, the code that       │
